  "name": "Deploy - Mobile Dashboard",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-mobile-dashboard\">Deploy - Mobile Dashboard</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy the Mobile Dashboard Feature once a signed solutions agreement/completed request form has been submitted:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enabling the Mobile Dashboard</span></p>\n<p> <img alt=\"rtaImage (48).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcMEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Login to clients Retail Express</p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Settings &gt; Global Settings</strong></p>\n<p>3. Select checkbox <strong>Mobile Dashboard</strong></p>\n<p>4. Click <strong>Save Changes</strong></p>\n<p>  </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (49).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powcREAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement/zendesk ticket</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Finance &gt; Mobile Dashboard Activated</strong></p>\n<p>4. Submit the ticket as <strong>Solved</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
